name: Unburner
body:
### Welcome to Unburner.
Unburner is a a Chrome extension to remove feedburner crap from links opened from Google Reader.

You can install it here [https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/nffehaffffkpgiloohpklpanbfhnkocb](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/nffehaffffkpgiloohpklpanbfhnkocb).
tagline: All the URL, none of the utm_source crapfest
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
